  </ul>
<% end %>
 
 
<p>If you have completed all of these forms, thank you! If any of your forms are<br> 
missing, please take a moment to click the links above and complete your <br>
enrollment forms.</p> 
 
<p>The Parent Agreement, Photo Consent and Liability Release may be completed <br>
once for your entire family.</p> 
 
<p>The Medical Form must be completed for each student enrolled at WEB. If your <br>
medical information will change before August 2023 (i.e. new insurance), you may <br>
omit this form until you have the required information.</p>
 
<p>Some 2023-24 WEB classes are full and many have waiting lists. Beginning May 3, <br>
students without completed forms (with the exception of medical forms) will be <br>
removed from rosters to make room for students on waiting lists.</p>
 
<p>If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to reach out.</p>
 
<p>
Thanks!
Senae Smith
